==English==

===Etymology===
From Latin ''[[antiquus]]'', old

===Pronunciation===
*{{IPA|/ænˈtiːk/}}
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-iːk|-iːk]]

===Adjective===
{{en-adj}}

# [[Old]], used especially of furniture and household items; out of date.

===Noun===
